# Set the default behavior, in case people don't have core.autocrlf set.
* text=auto

# Explicitly declare JavaScript/TypeScript files to always be LF on checkout
# and CRLF on Windows if desired, but "auto" usually handles this best.
# If you want to force LF in the repository:
*.js text eol=lf
*.ts text eol=lf
*.tsx text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
